heading_16 = heading_8 + ">>72. Tenancies"
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>(1) A cause of action of a person entitled to land subject to a periodic tenancy to recover the land from the tenant or from a; person claiming under the tenant accrues when the only or later of such of the following events as are applicable occurs ; person claiming under the tenant accrues when the only or later of such of the following events as are applicable occurs ; person claiming under the tenant accrues when the only or later of such of the following events as are applicable occurs ; person claiming under the tenant accrues when the only or later of such of the following events as are applicable occurs "
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>a"
