heading_11 = heading_9 + ">>9. Counselled offence, mode of execution immaterial"
CONTEXT(heading_11, 'When a person counsels another to commit an offence, and an offence is actually committed after such counsel by the person to whom it is given, it is immaterial whether the offence actually committed is the same as that counselled or a different one, or whether the offence is committed in the way counselled, or in a different way, provided in either case that the acts constituting the offence actually committed are a probable consequence of carrying out the counsel.')
heading_12 = heading_9 + ">>10. Term used accessory after the fact"
