heading_14 = heading_13 + ">>17. Previous conviction or acquittal a defence"
heading_15 = heading_14 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_15, 'It is a defence to a charge of any offence to show that the accused person has already been tried, and convicted or acquitted upon an indictment or prosecution notice on which he might have been convicted of the offence with which he is charged, or has already been convicted or acquitted of an offence of which he might be convicted upon the indictment or prosecution notice on which he is charged.')
heading_16 = heading_14 + ">>(2) Subsection (1) is subject to the; Criminal Appeals Act 2004 section 46M(4)(b) and (c).; Criminal Appeals Act 2004 section 46M(4)(b) and (c).; Criminal Appeals Act 2004 section 46M(4)(b) and (c)."
heading_17 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 17 amended No. 101 of 1990 s. 7 No. 84 of 2004 s. 80 No. 9 of 2012 s. 6.] [Chapter IV (s. 17A-17D, 18, 19, 19A, 19B, 20, 21, 21A) deleted No. 78 of 1995 s. 26.]; Chapter V  Criminal responsibility; Chapter V  Criminal responsibility; Chapter V  Criminal responsibility"
heading_18 = heading_17 + ">>22. Ignorance of law, honest claim of right"
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>content1"
CONTEXT(heading_19, 'Ignorance of the law does not afford any excuse for an act or omission which would otherwise constitute an offence, unless knowledge of the law by an offender is expressly declared to be an element of the offence.')
heading_20 = heading_18 + ">>content2"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'But a person is not criminally responsible, as for an offence relating to property, for an act done or omitted to be done by him with respect to any property in the exercise of an honest claim of right and without intention to defraud.')
heading_19 = heading_17 + ">>23. Intention and motive"
heading_20 = heading_19 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'Unless the intention to cause a particular result is expressly declared to be an element of the offence constituted, in whole or part, by an act or omission, the result intended to be caused by an act or omission is immaterial.')
heading_21 = heading_19 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'Unless otherwise expressly declared, the motive by which a person is induced to do or omit to do an act, or to form an intention, is immaterial so far as regards criminal responsibility.')
heading_18 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 23 inserted No. 29 of 2008 s. 4.]"
heading_19 = heading_18 + ">>23A. Unwilled acts and omissions"
heading_20 = heading_19 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_20, 'This section is subject to the provisions in Chapter XXVII and section 444A relating to negligent acts and omissions.')
heading_21 = heading_19 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'A person is not criminally responsible for an act or omission which occurs independently of the exercise of the persons will.')
heading_19 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 23A inserted No. 29 of 2008 s. 4 amended No. 43 of 2009 s. 6.]"
heading_20 = heading_19 + ">>23B. Accident"
heading_21 = heading_20 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_21, 'This section is subject to the provisions in Chapter XXVII and section 444A relating to negligent acts and omissions.')
heading_22 = heading_20 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'A person is not criminally responsible for an event which occurs by accident.')
heading_23 = heading_20 + ">>(3) If death or grievous bodily harm "
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'is directly caused to a victim by another persons act that involves a deliberate use of force but')
heading_25 = heading_23 + ">>(b) would not have occurred but for an abnormality, defect or weakness in the victim,"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'the other person is not, for that reason alone, excused from criminal responsibility for the death or grievous bodily harm.')
heading_24 = heading_20 + ">>(4) Subsection (3) applies "
heading_25 = heading_24 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'even if the other person did not intend or foresee the death or grievous bodily harm and')
heading_26 = heading_24 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_26, 'even if the death or grievous bodily harm was not reasonably foreseeable.')
heading_20 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 23B inserted No. 29 of 2008 s. 4 amended No. 43 of 2009 s. 7.]"
heading_21 = heading_20 + ">>24. Mistake of fact"
heading_22 = heading_21 + ">>content1"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'A person who does or omits to do an act under an honest and reasonable, but mistaken, belief in the existence of any state of things is not criminally responsible for the act or omission to any greater extent than if the real state of things had been such as he believed to exist.')
heading_23 = heading_21 + ">>content2"
CONTEXT(heading_23, 'The operation of this rule may be excluded by the express or implied provisions of the law relating to the subject.')
heading_22 = heading_20 + ">>25. Emergency"
heading_23 = heading_22 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_23, 'This section does not apply if section 32, 246, 247 or 248 applies.')
heading_24 = heading_22 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'A person is not criminally responsible for an act done, or an omission made, in an emergency under subsection (3).')
heading_25 = heading_22 + ">>(3) A person does an act or makes an omission in an emergency if "
heading_26 = heading_25 + ">>(a) the person believes "
heading_27 = heading_26 + ">>(i) circumstances of sudden or extraordinary emergency exist and"
heading_28 = heading_27 + ">>(ii) doing the act or making the omission is a necessary response to the emergency"
CONTEXT(heading_28, 'and')
heading_27 = heading_25 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_27, 'the act or omission is a reasonable response to the emergency in the circumstances as the person believes them to be and')
heading_28 = heading_25 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_28, 'there are reasonable grounds for those beliefs.')
heading_21 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 25 inserted No. 29 of 2008 s. 5.]"
heading_22 = heading_21 + ">>26. Presumption of sanity"
CONTEXT(heading_22, 'Every person is presumed to be of sound mind, and to have been of sound mind at any time which comes in question, until the contrary is proved.')
heading_23 = heading_21 + ">>27. Insanity"
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'A person is not criminally responsible for an act or omission on account of unsoundness of mind if at the time of doing the act or making the omission he is in such a state of mental impairment as to deprive him of capacity to understand what he is doing, or of capacity to control his actions, or of capacity to know that he ought not to do the act or make the omission.')
heading_25 = heading_23 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'A person whose mind, at the time of his doing or omitting to do an act, is affected by delusions on some specific matter or matters, but who is not otherwise entitled to the benefit of subsection (1), is criminally responsible for the act or omission to the same extent as if the real state of things had been such as he was induced by the delusions to believe to exist.')
heading_22 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 27 amended No. 69 of 1996 s. 7 No. 44 of 2009 s. 9.]"
heading_23 = heading_22 + ">>28. Intoxication"
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_24, 'Section 27 applies to the case of a person whose mind is disordered by intoxication or stupefaction caused without intention on his part by drugs or intoxicating liquor, or by any other means.')
heading_25 = heading_23 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'Section 27 does not apply to the case of a person who has intentionally caused himself to become intoxicated or stupefied, whether in order to afford excuse for the commission of an offence or not.')
heading_26 = heading_23 + ">>(3)"
CONTEXT(heading_26, 'When an intention to cause a specific result is an element of an offence, intoxication whether complete or partial, and whether intentional or unintentional, may be regarded for the purpose of ascertaining whether such an intention in fact existed.')
heading_23 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 28 amended No. 44 of 2009 s. 10.]"
heading_24 = heading_23 + ">>29. Immature age"
heading_25 = heading_24 + ">>content1"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'A person under the age of 10 years is not criminally responsible for any act or omission.')
heading_26 = heading_24 + ">>content2"
CONTEXT(heading_26, 'A person under the age of 14 years is not criminally responsible for an act or omission, unless it is proved that at the time of doing the act or making the omission he had capacity to know that he ought not to do the act or make the omission.')
heading_24 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 29 amended No. 74 of 1985 s. 4 No. 49 of 1988 s. 44.]"
heading_25 = heading_24 + ">>30. Judicial officers"
CONTEXT(heading_25, 'Except as expressly provided by this Code, a judicial officer is not criminally responsible for anything done or omitted to be done by him in the exercise of his judicial functions, although the act done is in excess of his judicial authority, or although he is bound to do the act omitted to be done.')
heading_26 = heading_24 + ">>31. Lawful authority"
heading_27 = heading_26 + ">>(1) A person is not criminally responsible for an act done, or an omission made, in any of the following circumstances "
heading_28 = heading_27 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_28, 'in execution of the law')
heading_29 = heading_27 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_29, 'in obedience to the order of a competent authority which the person is bound by law to obey, unless the order is manifestly unlawful.')
heading_28 = heading_26 + ">>(2)"
CONTEXT(heading_28, 'Whether an order is or is not manifestly unlawful is a question of law.')
heading_25 = heading_16 + ">>[Section 31 inserted No. 29 of 2008 s. 6.]"
heading_26 = heading_25 + ">>32. Duress"
heading_27 = heading_26 + ">>(1)"
CONTEXT(heading_27, 'A person is not criminally responsible for an act done, or an omission made, under duress under subsection (2).')
heading_28 = heading_26 + ">>(2) A person does an act or makes an omission under duress if "
heading_29 = heading_28 + ">>(a) the person believes "
heading_30 = heading_29 + ">>(i) a threat has been made and"
heading_31 = heading_30 + ">>(ii) the threat will be carried out unless an offence is committed and  (iii) doing the act or making the omission is necessary to prevent the threat from being carried out"
CONTEXT(heading_31, 'and')
heading_30 = heading_28 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_30, 'the act or omission is a reasonable response to the threat in the circumstances as the person believes them to be and')
heading_31 = heading_28 + ">>c"
CONTEXT(heading_31, 'there are reasonable grounds for those beliefs.')
heading_29 = heading_26 + ">>(3) Subsections (1) and (2) do not apply if the threat is made by or on behalf of a person with whom the person under duress is voluntarily associating for the purpose of "
heading_30 = heading_29 + ">>a"
CONTEXT(heading_30, 'doing an act or making an omission of the kind in fact done or made by the person under duress or')
heading_31 = heading_29 + ">>b"
CONTEXT(heading_31, 'prosecuting an unlawful purpose in which it is reasonably foreseeable such a threat would be made.')
